Request attributes:
-------------------
:id, :channel, :preferences


Channel attributes:
-------------------
:id, :language, :country, :category, :preferences

Advert attributes
-----------------
:name, :start-date, :end-date, :category, :country, :language

Design:
-------
* Rule
 - Operands
 - Operators

* Rule Evaluator
  * bind request to rule
  * bind ad to rule
  * evaluate / interpret
  * returns true | false

* All Ads which eval to true are picked

* Update counters and other book keeping information / metrics
